    {
      "id": "j501-any-agent",
      "type": "MARKDOWN",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "## 7. Any Agentic System — Quick Reference\n\n### HTTP Direct (works with any agent that can make HTTP calls)\n\n```bash\n# Health check\ncurl http://localhost:8585/api/settings/status\n\n# List notebooks\ncurl http://localhost:8585/api/notebooks\n\n# Execute Java code\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8585/api/shell/execute \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d '{\"sessionId\":\"agent-1\",\"code\":\"System.out.println(42);\"}'\n\n# Create notebook\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8585/api/notebooks \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d '{\"name\":\"My Agent Notebook\"}'\n```\n\n### MCP Protocol (for MCP-compatible agents)\n\n```bash\n# Initialize\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8585/api/mcp/messages \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"method\":\"initialize\",\"params\":{\"protocolVersion\":\"2024-11-05\",\"clientInfo\":{\"name\":\"my-agent\",\"version\":\"1.0\"}}}'\n\n# List tools\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8585/api/mcp/messages \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"method\":\"tools/list\",\"params\":{}}'\n\n# Call a tool\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8585/api/mcp/messages \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":3,\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"venus_execute_code\",\"arguments\":{\"code\":\"42 * 2\",\"session\":\"demo\"}}}'\n```",
      "output": "",
