    {
      "id": "j501-footer",
      "type": "MARKDOWN",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "---\n\n## Summary — Venus as an Agentic Platform\n\n| Capability | MCP Tool | REST Endpoint |\n|---|---|---|\n| Execute Java | `venus_execute_code` | `POST /api/shell/execute` |\n| List notebooks | `venus_list_notebooks` | `GET /api/notebooks` |\n| Read notebook | `venus_read_notebook` | `GET /api/notebooks/{id}` |\n| Run pipeline | `venus_run_pipeline` | `POST /api/shell/execute-pipeline` |\n| Search cells | `venus_search_cells` | *(search via read + filter)* |\n| Load module | `venus_load_module` | *(orchestration endpoint)* |\n| **Create notebook** | `venus_create_notebook` | `POST /api/notebooks` |\n| **Add cell** | `venus_append_cell` | `PUT /api/notebooks/{id}` |\n\nVenus turns your local Java knowledge base into a **live, queryable, executable tool** for any AI agent — no cloud required.",
